Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Namuac Elementary School in Barangay San Andres, Municipality of Sanchez Mira, Province of Cagayan, to Namuac-San Andres Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 861
An Act Changing the Name of the Namuac Elementary School in Barangay San Andres, Municipality of Sanchez Mira, Province of Cagayan, to Namuac-San Andres Elementary School
Section 1. The name of the Namuac Elementary School in Barangay San Andres, Municipality of Sanchez Mira, Province of Cagayan, is changed to Namuac-San Andres Elementary School.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 27, 1984
